# Exemplos da literatura
The role of spatial and environmental variables in shaping aquatic insect assemblages in two protected areas in the transition area between Cerrado and Amazônia &lt;em&gt;Biota Neotrop. vol.20 no.3 Campinas 2020 Epub June 24, 2020&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;http://dx.doi.org/10.1590/1676-0611-bn-2019-0923&#34; class=&#34;uri&#34;&gt;http://dx.doi.org/10.1590/1676-0611-bn-2019-0923&lt;/a&gt;
.center[
&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.scielo.br/img/revistas/bn/v20n3//1676-0611-bn-20-03-e20190932-gf03.jpg&#34;  width=&#34;70%&#34; /&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;
